sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant P as Panel/Popup
  participant C as Content Script
  participant B as Background (SW)
  participant O as Offscreen Doc
  participant D as Downloads

  Note over U,D: Full Page export
  U->>P: Click "Export Full Page"
  P->>B: RunExport(fullPage)
  B->>C: CollectPageArtifacts
  C-->>B: {html, css, js}
  loop for each viewport step
    B->>B: captureVisibleTab
    B->>O: AddFrame(dataUrl, y)
  end
  O-->>B: StitchedPng
  B->>B: JSZip.assemble
  B->>D: download(zip)
  B-->>P: status=success

  Note over U,D: Element export
  U->>P: Click "Pick Element"
  P->>C: EnterPickerMode
  U->>C: Hover + right-click
  C->>B: ExportElement(rect, selector)
  B->>B: captureVisibleTab (context)
  B->>O: CropToRect
  C->>O: RenderIsolated(clone+css)
  O-->>B: {contextPng, isolatedPng}
  B->>B: buildMarkdown
  B->>D: download(md)
  B-->>P: status=success
